2️⃣ Direct Addressing

Address is given.

3️⃣ Indirect Addressing

Address points to another address.

4️⃣ Register Addressing

Operand in register.

5️⃣ Register Indirect

Register holds memory address.

6️⃣ Indexed Addressing

Address + index register.

📌 GATE Favorite: Identify addressing mode.

🔹 Instruction Set Architecture (ISA)

Defines:

Instructions
Registers
Addressing modes

📌 Interface between hardware & software.

🔹 Common GATE Traps
Mixing addressing modes
Confusing fetch-decode-execute order
Misinterpreting operand vs opcode
